Use hexdump to ARP request message to determine the following:
a. The HW type
b. The protocol type
c. The HW length
d. The protocol length
e. The value of the operation field and its type
f. The src HW address
g. The src protocol address
h. The dest HW address (both in request and in reply)
i. The dest protocol address
j. Check for the presence of any ICMP message 